Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I believe in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}America has made my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I raised my daughter\Nin the American fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I gave her freedom, but I taught her\Nnever to dishonour her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She found a boyfriend, not an Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She went to the movies with him.\NShe stayed out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I didn't protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Two months ago he took her for a drive\Nwith another boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They made her drink whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and then they tried to\Ntake advantage of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She resisted, she kept her honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So they beat her like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When I went to the hospital,\Nher nose was broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}her jaw was shattered,\Nheld together by wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She couldn't even weep\Nbecause of the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I wept. Why did I weep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She was the light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now she will never be beautiful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I went to the police,\Nlike a good American.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}These two boys were brought to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The judge sentenced them to three years\Nin prison, but suspended the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Suspended the sentence!\NThey went free that very day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I stood in the courtroom like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Those two bastards, they smiled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then I said to my wife, "For justice,\Nwe must go to Don Corleone."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why did you go to the police?\NWhy didn't you come to me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What do you want of me? Tell me\Nanything, but do what I beg you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want them dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll give you anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I've known you many years, but this\Nis the first time you've asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I can't remember the last time\Nyou invited me for a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Even though my wife is godmother\Nto your only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But let's be frank here.\NYou never wanted my friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And you were afraid to be in my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I didn't want to get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You found Paradise in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You made a good living, had police\Nprotection and there were courts of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You didn't need a friend like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But now you come to me and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}"Don Corleone, give me justice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But you don't ask with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You don't offer friendship. You don't\Neven think to call me Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You come on my daughter's wedding\Nday and ask me to murder for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I ask you for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That is not justice.\NYour daughter is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let them suffer, then, as she suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How much shall I pay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Bonasera, Bonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What have I ever done to make you\Ntreat me so disrespectfully?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you'd come in friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}the scum that ruined your daughter\Nwould be suffering this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And if an honest man like you should\Nmake enemies, they'd be my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And then they would fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Godfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Some day, and that day may never\Ncome, I'll ask a service of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But until that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...accept this justice as a gift\Non my daughter's wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Grazie, Godfather.\N- Prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Give this to Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want people that aren't going to\Nget carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're not murderers,\Nin spite of what this undertaker says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Where's Michael?\N- Don't worry, he'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're not taking the picture\Nwithout Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's the matter?\N- It's Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, Paulie! Let me have some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Paulie! More wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You look terrific on the floor.\N- Are you a dance judge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take a walk and do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sandra, watch the kids.\NDon't let them run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You watch yourself, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}20, 30 grand. In small bills, cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In that little silk purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If this were somebody else's wedding...\NSfortunato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Have to go back to work.\N- Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No Sicilian can refuse any request\Non his daughter's wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone, I'm honoured and\Ngrateful that you have invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get out of here!\NIt's a private party. Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What is it? It's my sister's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Goddamn FBI don't respect nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come here, come here, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...but towards the end, he was paroled\Nto help with the American war effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}so for six months he's worked\Nin my pastry shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nazorine, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now that the war is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}this boy, Enzo, they want to\Nrepatriate him back to Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Godfather, I have a daughter.\NYou see, she and Enzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You want Enzo to stay in this country,\Nand your daughter to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mr Hagen. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Wait till you see the wedding cake\NI made for your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The bride, the groom and the angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Who should I give this job to?\N- Not to our paisá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Give it to a Jew Congressman in\Nanother district. Who else is on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's not on the list,\Nbut Luca Brasi wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Is this necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He didn't expect to be invited to the\Nwedding, so he wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone, I'm honoured and\Ngrateful that you have invited me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}on the wedding day of your daughter.\NMay their first child be a masculine child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That man over there\Nis talking to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}See that scary guy over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He's a very scary guy.\N- What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}His name is Luca Brasi.\NHe helps my father out sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael, he's coming over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You look terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My brother Tom Hagen,\NMiss Kay Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your father's been asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Very nice to meet you.\N- Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why does your brother\Nhave a different name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My brother Sonny found Tom Hagen\Nin the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He had no home,\Nso my father took him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's been with us ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Not a Sicilian. I think he's\Ngoing to be consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's that?\N- That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...Iike a counsellor, an advisor.\NVery important for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You like your lasagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm honoured and grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}that you have invited me\Nto your daughter's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}On the day of your daughter's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:15:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I hope that their first child\Nwill be a masculine child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I pledge my ever-ending loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- For your daughter's bridal purse.\N- Thank you, Luca. Most valued friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone, I'm going to leave you\Nnow, because I know you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Signora Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Senator Cauley apologised for not\Ncoming, but said you'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Also some of the judges.\NThey've all sent gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What is that outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Johnny! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He came all the way from California.\NI told you he'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He's probably in trouble again.\N- He's a good godson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Johnny, Johnny! Sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You never said you knew\NJohnny Fontane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sure. You want to meet him?\N- Great! Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- My father helped him with his career.\N- He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Let's listen to this song.\N- Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Please, Michael. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When Johnny was starting out, he was\Nsigned to a personal service contract
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}with a big bandleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And as his career got better and better,\Nhe wanted to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Johnny is my father's godson.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My father went to see this bandleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He offered him 10,000 dollars\Nto let Johnny go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}but the bandleader said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So the next day my father went to see\Nhim, but this time with Luca Brasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Within an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}he signed a release\Nfor a certified cheque of 1,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How did he do that?\N- Made him an offer he couldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What was that?\N- Luca Brasi held a gun to his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and father said that either his brains or\Nhis signature would be on the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's a true story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's my family, Kay. It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to find Santino.\NTell him to come to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How are you, Fredo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My brother Fredo,\Nthis is Kay Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hi.\N- How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- This is my brother Mike.\N- Are you having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah. This is your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't know what to do.\NMy voice is weak. It's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Anyway, if I had this part in the picture,\Nit puts me right back on top again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But this... man won't give it to me,\Nthe head of the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's his name?\N- Woltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He won't give it to me,\Nand he says there's no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sonny, are you in there?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:22:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The old man wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A month ago he bought the movie rights\Nto this book, a best-seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The main character\Nis a guy just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I wouldn't even have to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Godfather, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You can act like a man!\NWhat's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Is this how you turned out a Hollywood\Nfinocchio, that cries like a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}"What can I do? What can I do?"\NWhat is that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You spend time with your family?\N- Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Because a man who doesn't spend time\Nwith his family can never be a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You look terrible. I want you to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Rest, and in a month this Hollywood\Nbig shot will give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's too late, they start shooting\Nin a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.45,0:24:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm going to make him an offer\Nhe can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.33,0:24:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Just go outside and enjoy yourself,\Nand forget about all this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I want you to leave it all to me.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.70,0:25:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What time does my daughter leave?\N- Soon, after they cut the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.08,0:25:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do we give your son-in-law\Nsomething important?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Never. Give him a living, but never\Ndiscuss the family business with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What else?\N- Virgil Sollozzo called.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- We'll have to see him next week.\N- When you come back from California.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.77,0:25:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- When am I going to California?\N- Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.06,0:25:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to talk to this movie big shot\Nand settle this business for Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If there's nothing else, I'd like to go\Nto my daughter's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.03,0:25:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Carlo, we're going to take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.12,0:25:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.21,0:25:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, Michael. Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Okay, that's it. Just like that. Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.83,0:27:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You need a little more heat on that arc.\N- Start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.87,0:27:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I was sent by a friend\Nof Johnny Fontane.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This friend would give\Nhis friendship to Mr Woltz,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:28:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}if Mr Woltz would grant us a favour.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.34,0:28:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Woltz is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.80,0:28:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Give Johnny the part in that war film\Nyou're starting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.48,0:28:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And what favour would your friend\Ngrant Mr Woltz?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.65,0:28:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He could make your future union\Nproblems disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.28,0:28:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And one of your stars has just moved\Nfrom marijuana to heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.41,0:28:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Are you trying to muscle me?\NListen, you son-of-a-bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.79,0:28:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let me lay it on the line. Johnny\NFontane will never get that movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.62,0:28:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No matter how many Dago Guinea\Ngreaseballs come out of the woodwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.21,0:28:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm German-Irish.\N- Listen here, my Kraut-Mick friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.18,0:28:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm going to make trouble for you!\N- I'm a lawyer. I haven't threatened...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.76,0:28:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I know New York's big lawyers.\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.06,0:28:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have a special practice. I handle\None client. I'll wait for your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.32,0:29:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}By the way, I admire your pictures\Nvery much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.07,0:29:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Check him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- It's really beautiful.\N- Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.81,0:29:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- It used to decorate a king's palace.\N- Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.48,0:29:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why didn't you say\Nyou work for Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.36,0:29:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I thought you were some cheap hustler\NJohnny was running in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.65,0:29:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I only use his name when necessary.\N- How's your drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.78,0:29:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Fine.\N- Now I'll show you something beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You do appreciate beauty, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.75,0:30:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There you are.\N600,000 dollars on four hoofs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.04,0:30:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I bet Russian czars never paid\Nthat for a single horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.96,0:30:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Khartoum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.26,0:30:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Khartoum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.80,0:30:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm not going to race him, though.\NI'm going to put him out to stud.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.89,0:30:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Thanks, Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.64,0:30:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Corleone is Johnny's godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.69,0:30:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}To the Italian people that's\Na very sacred, close relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.20,0:30:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I respect it. Tell him to ask me anything\Nelse. This favour I can't give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.04,0:30:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He never asks a second favour\Nwhen he's been refused the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You don't understand. Johnny Fontane\Nnever gets that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.25,0:30:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That part is perfect for him.\NIt'll make him a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.30,0:30:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm going to run him out of the business,\Nand let me tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.06,0:30:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Johnny Fontane ruined one of Woltz\NInternational's most valuable protégés.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We trained her for five years.\NSinging, acting, dancing lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.48,0:31:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I spent hundreds of thousands of dollars\Non her, to make her a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.28,0:31:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let me be even more frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.03,0:31:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}To show you that I'm not a hard-hearted\Nman. That it's not all dollars and cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She was beautiful.\NShe was young and innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.87,0:31:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She's the greatest piece of ass I've had\Nand I've had them all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.25,0:31:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then Johnny Fontane comes along with\Nhis olive oil voice and Guinea charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.59,0:31:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And she runs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.39,0:31:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She threw it all away\Njust to make me look ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.56,0:31:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And a man in my position can't afford\Nto be made to look ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.11,0:31:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If that goombah tries any rough stuff,\Ntell him I'm no bandleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.95,0:31:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah, I heard that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.95,0:32:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Thank you for dinner\Nand a very pleasant evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.96,0:32:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Maybe your car can take me\Nto the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.75,0:32:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mr Corleone insists on hearing\Nbad news immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.12,0:34:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You're not too tired, are you, Tom?\N- No, I slept on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.33,0:34:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have the Sollozzo notes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.54,0:34:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sollozzo is known as The Turk. He's\Nsupposed to be very good with a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.55,0:34:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}but only in matters of business\Nwith reasonable complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.89,0:34:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}His business is narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.18,0:34:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He has fields in Turkey,\Nwhere they grow poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In Sicily he has plants to process them\Ninto heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.65,0:34:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He needs cash, he needs protection\Nfrom the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.44,0:34:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He'll give a piece of the action.\NI don't know how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.32,0:34:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The Tattaglia family is behind him here.\NThey have to be in it for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.75,0:34:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What about his prison record?\N- One term in Italy, one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.42,0:34:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's known as a top narcotics man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.21,0:34:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Santino, what do you think?\N- A lot of money in that white powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.26,0:35:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.89,0:35:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yes. There's more money in narcotics\Nthan anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.02,0:35:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If we don't get into it, somebody else\Nwill, maybe the five families.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.81,0:35:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}With that money they can buy\Nmore police and political power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then they come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.69,0:35:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now we have unions and gambling, and\Nthat's great, but narcotics is the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.95,0:35:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If we don't get a piece of that action,\Nwe risk everything in ten years' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.71,0:35:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So? What's your answer\Ngoing to be, Pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.72,0:35:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.51,0:35:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I need a man who has powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.02,0:35:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I need a million dollars in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.77,0:35:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I need those politicians that you carry\Nin your pocket, like nickels and dimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.94,0:36:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What is the interest for my family?\N- 30 per cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.16,0:36:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In the first year your end should be\Nthree, four million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.49,0:36:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And then it would go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.41,0:36:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And what is the interest\Nfor the Tattaglia family?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.75,0:36:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.22,0:36:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll take care of them, out of my share.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.22,0:36:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So I receive 30 per cent for finance,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.18,0:36:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}political influence and legal protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.69,0:36:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why do you come to me?\NWhy do I deserve this generosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you consider a million dollars in cash\Njust finance,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.95,0:36:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}ti saluto, Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.42,0:37:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I said that I would see you, because\NI heard you were a serious man,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.88,0:37:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}to be treated with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.85,0:37:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But, I must say no to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I'll give you my reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's true, I have a lot of friends in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They wouldn't be friendly long if I was\Ninvolved in drugs instead of gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.24,0:37:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}which they regard as a harmless vice,\Nbut drugs is a dirty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.91,0:37:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It doesn't make any difference to me\Nwhat a man does for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But your business is...\Na little dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.17,0:37:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you're worried about security,\Nthe Tattaglias will guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.43,0:37:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- The Tattaglias would guarantee our...\N- Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.98,0:38:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have a sentimental weakness\Nfor my children, and I spoil them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.07,0:38:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They talk when they should listen.\NBut anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.99,0:38:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Signor Sollozzo, my no is final. I wish to\Ncongratulate you on your new business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.37,0:38:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I know you'll do well, and good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.58,0:38:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Especially since your interests\Ndon't conflict with mine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.06,0:38:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Santino.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.19,0:38:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.07,0:38:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter with you? Your brain\Nis going soft from playing with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.03,0:38:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Never tell anybody outside the family\Nwhat you're thinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.29,0:39:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.55,0:39:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom, what's this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.67,0:39:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's from Johnny.\NHe's starring in that new film.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.14,0:39:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Take it away.\N- Take it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.27,0:39:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.73,0:39:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...tell Luca Brasi to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.99,0:39:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm a little worried\Nabout this Sollozzo fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.61,0:39:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Find out what he's got\Nunder his fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.49,0:39:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go to the Tattaglias.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.16,0:39:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Make them think that you're not\Ntoo happy with our family
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.79,0:39:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and find out what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.61,0:40:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I got something for your mother\Nand for Sonny
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.11,0:40:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and a tie for Freddy,\Nand Tom Hagen got the Reynolds pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.99,0:40:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What do you want for Christmas?\N- Just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.86,0:40:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Andiamo, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Tell Paulie to get the car.\N- Okay, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.65,0:40:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll have to get it myself.\NPaulie called in sick this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.20,0:41:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Paulie's a good kid.\NI don't mind getting the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.96,0:41:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Buon Natale, caro. Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.71,0:41:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Luca! I'm Bruno Tattaglia.\N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.77,0:42:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.31,0:42:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.31,0:42:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You have been talking to the\NTattaglia family...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.07,0:42:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I think you and I can do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.57,0:42:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I need someone strong like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.28,0:42:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I heard you are not happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.00,0:42:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...with the Corleone family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.42,0:42:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Want to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.17,0:42:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.67,0:42:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}$50,000 to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.76,0:42:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.27,0:42:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.08,0:43:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom! Tom Hagen. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.08,0:43:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Glad to see you. I want to talk to you.\N- I haven't got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.96,0:43:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Make time, Consigliere. Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.84,0:44:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What are you worried about? If I wanted\Nto kill you, you'd be dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.72,0:44:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.32,0:44:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Fredo, I'm going to buy some fruit.\N- Okay, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.16,0:44:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Merry Christmas. I want some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.67,0:46:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Would you like me better\Nif I were a nun? Like in the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.47,0:46:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What if I were Ingrid Bergman?\N- Now, that's a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.93,0:46:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.93,0:46:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, I wouldn't like you better if you were\NIngrid Bergman. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.20,0:46:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They don't say if he's dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.10,0:47:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sonny, it's Michael.\N- Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.57,0:47:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Is he all right?\N- We don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.40,0:47:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There are all kinds of stories.\NHe was hit bad, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.28,0:47:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Are you there?\N- Yeah, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.66,0:47:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Where have you been? I was worried.\N- Didn't Tom tell you I called?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.25,0:47:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No. Look, come home, kid.\NYou should be with Mama, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.18,0:47:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.85,0:47:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.07,0:47:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Stay back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.49,0:47:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Who is it?\N- Open up, it's Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.53,0:47:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There's more news about your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.87,0:48:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Word is out that he's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.79,0:48:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's the matter with you?\N- Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.63,0:48:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Where was Paulie?\N- Sick. He's been sick all winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.05,0:48:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How often?\N- Only three, four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.80,0:48:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Freddy didn't want a new bodyguard.\N- Pick him up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.72,0:48:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't care how sick he is. Bring him\Nto my father's house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.35,0:48:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You want anyone sent over here?\N- No. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.86,0:48:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm going to have a couple of our people\Ncome over to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.29,0:48:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hello?\N- Santino Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.79,0:48:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Yeah.\N- We have Tom Hagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.83,0:48:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In three hours he'll be released\Nwith our proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.42,0:48:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Listen to what he has to say\Nbefore you do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's done is done. Don't lose that\Nfamous temper of yours, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.68,0:48:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.53,0:49:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your boss is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.41,0:49:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I know you're not in the muscle end\Nof the family, so don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.79,0:49:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to help the Corleones\Nand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.71,0:49:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We got him outside his office\Nabout an hour after we picked you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.80,0:49:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.64,0:49:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's up to you to make peace\Nbetween me and Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.48,0:49:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny was hot for my deal, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.65,0:49:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And you knew\Nit was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.57,0:50:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sonny will come after you.\N- That will be his first reaction, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.12,0:50:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So you have to talk sense into him.\NThe Tattaglia family is behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.67,0:50:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The other New York families will go\Nalong with anything to prevent war.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.05,0:50:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's face it, with all due respect,\Nthe Don - rest in peace - was slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.10,0:50:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Ten years ago,\Ncould I have gotten to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.98,0:50:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, now he's dead, Tom,\Nand nothing can bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.70,0:50:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You've got to talk to Sonny, to the\NCaporegimes, Tessio, fat Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.50,0:50:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's good business, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.13,0:50:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll try. But even Sonny won't be able\Nto call off Luca Brasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.97,0:51:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.51,0:51:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let me worry about Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.11,0:51:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You just talk to Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.40,0:51:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And the other two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.82,0:51:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'll do my best.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.70,0:51:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't like violence, Tom.\NI'm a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.84,0:51:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Blood is a big expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.32,0:52:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.57,0:52:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They hit him with five shots,\Nand he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.49,0:52:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's bad luck for me, and bad luck\Nfor you if you don't make that deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.71,0:53:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your mother is at the hospital with\Nyour father. Looks like he'll pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.55,0:53:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's a lot of bad blood. Sollozzo, Philip\NTattaglia, Bruno Tattaglia, Ramon...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.27,0:53:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You gonna kill all those guys?\N- Stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.35,0:53:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you get rid of Sollozzo,\Neverything falls into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.52,0:53:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What about Luca?\NSollozzo thinks he can control him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.57,0:53:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If Luca sold out, we're in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.66,0:53:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Has anyone been in touch with Luca?\N- We've been trying all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.62,0:53:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hey, do me a favour...\N- Luca never sleeps over with a broad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.37,0:53:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, Tom, you're consigliere.\NWhat do we do if the old man dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.75,0:53:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If we lose the old man, we lose the\Npolitical contacts and half our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.22,0:53:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The other New York families might\Nsupport Sollozzo to avoid a long war.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.68,0:53:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This is almost 1946.\NNobody wants bloodshed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.40,0:53:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If your father dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.32,0:54:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...you make the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.28,0:54:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Easy to say. He's not your father.\N- I'm as much a son as you or Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.54,0:54:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.12,0:54:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Paulie, I told you to stay put.\N- The guy at the gates has a package.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.50,0:54:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tessio, go see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.47,0:54:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Shall I stay?\N- Yeah. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.93,0:54:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm fine.\N- There's food. Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.81,0:54:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- No.\N- A drink? Brandy will sweat it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.48,0:54:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Go ahead.\N- That might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.73,0:54:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take care of that son-of-a-bitch.\NPaulie sold out the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.99,0:54:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Make that the first thing on your list.\N- Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.53,0:54:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mickey, tomorrow, get some guys\Nand go to Luca's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.08,0:54:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Maybe we shouldn't get Mike\Nmixed up in this too directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.00,0:55:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hanging around the house on\Nthe phone would be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.55,0:55:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Try Luca again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.52,0:55:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's this?\N- A Sicilian message.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.52,0:55:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It means Luca Brasi\Nsleeps with the fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.16,0:55:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm going.\N- When will you be home?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.62,0:55:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Probably late.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.38,0:55:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Don't forget the cannoli!\N- Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.30,0:55:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Rocco, sit on the other side.\NYou block the rear-view mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.22,0:55:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny's running wild. He wants\Nto go to mattresses already.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.18,0:56:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We have to find a spot on the\NWest Side. Try 309 West 43rd Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.86,0:56:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Know a good spot on the West Side?\N- I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.57,0:56:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Think while you're driving.\NI want to hit New York this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.36,0:56:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Watch the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.83,0:56:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Paulie, go down 39th Street, pick up\N18 mattresses and bring me the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.80,0:56:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.43,0:56:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Make sure they're clean, because\Nthe guys will be there a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.06,0:56:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- They're clean and exterminated.\N- That's a bad word to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.39,0:56:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Exterminate! Watch out,\Nso we don't exterminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.03,0:56:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Pull over. I've got to take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.45,0:57:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Leave the gun. Take the cannoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.93,0:58:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, Mike! Hey, Mikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.60,0:58:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Yeah.\N- Phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.82,0:58:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Who is it?\N- Some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.49,0:58:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hello. Kay?\N- How's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.99,0:58:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.41,0:58:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.12,0:58:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.04,0:58:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Michael?\N- Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.75,0:58:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Tell me you love me.\N- I can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.76,0:58:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Can't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.80,0:58:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.47,0:58:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why don't you tell that nice girl\Nyou love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.76,0:58:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I love you with all my heart. If I don't\Nsee you again soon, I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.60,0:58:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come and learn something. You might\Nhave to cook for 20 guys some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.53,0:58:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You start with a little oil,\Nthen fry some garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.36,0:59:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Throw in some tomatoes, tomato paste,\Nfry it and make sure it doesn't stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.87,0:59:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You get it to a boil, you shove in\Nall your sausage and meatballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.87,0:59:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Add a little bit of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.17,0:59:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And a little bit of sugar. That's my trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.88,0:59:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Cut the crap. I have more important\Nthings for you. How's Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.35,0:59:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You won't see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.60,0:59:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Where are you going?\N- To the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.56,0:59:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Send bodyguards with him.\N- I'm going to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.15,0:59:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He'll be all right. Sollozzo knows\Nhe's a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.53,0:59:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Be careful.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.57,0:59:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Send somebody with him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.15,1:00:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I have to go.\N- Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.69,1:00:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, Kay. There will be detectives there,\Npeople from the press.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.36,1:00:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll wait in the cab.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.83,1:00:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't want you to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.21,1:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When will I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.76,1:00:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go back to New Hampshire, and I'll\Ncall you at your parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.60,1:00:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- When will I see you again, Michael?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.36,1:03:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What are you doing here?\NYou're not supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.61,1:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm Michael Corleone. This is my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.91,1:03:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What happened to the guards?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.91,1:03:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your father had too many visitors.\NThey interfered with hospital service.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.29,1:03:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The police made them leave\Nabout ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.76,1:03:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get me Long Beach 45620, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.39,1:03:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nurse. Wait a minute. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.77,1:03:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny, I'm at the hospital.\NI got here late, there's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.77,1:03:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No Tessio's men, no detectives,\Nnobody. Papa's all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.99,1:03:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Don't panic.\N- I won't panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.99,1:03:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm sorry, but you will have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.66,1:04:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're going to move him to another\Nroom. Can you disconnect the tubes?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.59,1:04:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- That's out of the question!\N- Do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.30,1:04:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Men are coming here to kill him.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.63,1:04:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.46,1:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Who are you?\N- I am Enzo, the baker.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.30,1:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Remember me?\N- Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.64,1:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You'd better go,\Nthere's going to be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.72,1:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If there is trouble, I'll stay here to\Nhelp you. For your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.60,1:05:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Listen. Wait for me outside,\Nin front of the hospital, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.61,1:05:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll be out in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.58,1:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Just lie here, Pop.\NI'll take care of you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.09,1:06:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm with you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.72,1:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.76,1:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get rid of these. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.88,1:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Put your hand in your pocket, like you\Nhave a gun. You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.65,1:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.82,1:08:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I thought all you Guinea hoods\Nwere locked up!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.37,1:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Why isn't anyone guarding my father?\N- You little punk!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.79,1:08:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't you tell me my business!\NI pulled them off.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.04,1:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Stay away from this hospital!\N- Not until my father's room is guarded.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.63,1:09:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Phil, take him in!\N- The kid's clean, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.93,1:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He's a war hero. He's never been...\N- I said take him in!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's The Turk paying you?\N- Take a hold of him. Stand him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.19,1:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Stand him up straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.26,1:09:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm the Corleone's attorney. These men\Nare hired to protect Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.43,1:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They're licensed to carry firearms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.01,1:09:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you interfere, you'll have to appear\Nbefore the judge and show cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.27,1:09:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.55,1:10:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's with all the new faces?\N- We'll need them now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.52,1:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}After the hospital thing, Sonny got mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.39,1:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We hit Bruno Tattaglia this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.56,1:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.32,1:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Looks like a fortress around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.12,1:10:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tommasuccio! Hey... 100 buttonmen\Non the street 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.46,1:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That Turk shows one hair on his ass,\Nhe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.21,1:11:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mike, let me look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.22,1:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You're beautiful, beautiful.\NYou're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.60,1:11:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The Turk wants to talk! Imagine\Nthe nerve of the son-of-a-bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.23,1:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He wants a meeting today.\N- What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.27,1:11:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What did he say... He wants us to send\NMichael to hear the proposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.82,1:11:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He promises that the deal\Nis too good to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.24,1:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- And Bruno Tattaglia?\N- That's part of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He cancels out what they did to Father.\N- We should listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.16,1:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No more! Not this time, Consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.46,1:11:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No more meetings, discussions,\Nor Sollozzo tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.88,1:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want Sollozzo, or we go to war...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.17,1:11:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- The other families...\N- They hand me Sollozzo!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.05,1:11:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This is business, not personal!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.93,1:11:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- They shot my father...\N- Even that was business, not personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.81,1:12:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then business will have to suffer.\NDo me a favour.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.61,1:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No more advice on how to\Npatch things up. Just help me win.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.91,1:12:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I found out about Captain McCluskey,\Nwho broke Mike's jaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.87,1:12:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's definitely on Sollozzo's payroll,\Nand for big money.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.33,1:12:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}McCluskey has agreed to be\NThe Turk's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.38,1:12:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So when Sollozzo is being guarded,\Nhe's invulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.22,1:12:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nobody has ever gunned down\Na New York police captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.01,1:12:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All the families would come after you.\NThe Corleone family would be outcasts!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.98,1:12:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Even the old man's political protection\Nwould run for cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.06,1:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do me a favour.\NTake this into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.86,1:12:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All right, we'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.87,1:13:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We can't wait. We can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.29,1:13:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No matter what Sollozzo says,\Nhe's going to kill Pop.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.42,1:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's the key for him.\NWe've got to get Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.42,1:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Mike is right.\N- Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.76,1:13:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What about this McCluskey?\NWhat do we do with this cop?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.40,1:13:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They want to have a meeting\Nwith me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.03,1:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It will be me, McCluskey and Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.57,1:13:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's set the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.70,1:13:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get our informers to find out\Nwhere it's going to be held.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.29,1:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We insist it's a public place.\NA bar, a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.34,1:13:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Some place where there are people,\Nso I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.59,1:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They'll search me when I meet them,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.76,1:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So I can't have a weapon on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.48,1:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But if Clemenza can figure out a way to\Nhave a weapon planted there for me...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.45,1:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...then I'll kill them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.88,1:14:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nice college boy. Didn't want to\Nget mixed up in the family business.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.80,1:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now you want to shoot a police captain\Nbecause he slapped you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.55,1:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This isn't like the army! You have to get\Nclose and get their brains on your suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.18,1:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You're taking this very personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.15,1:14:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom, this is business\Nand he's taking it personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.69,1:14:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Where does it say you can't kill a cop?\N- Mikey...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.65,1:15:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm talking about a cop who's mixed up\Nin drugs, a dishonest cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.33,1:15:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A cop who got mixed up in the rackets\Nand got what was coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.54,1:15:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's a terrific story. We have\Nnewspaper people on the payroll, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.75,1:15:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- They might like a story like that.\N- They might.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.18,1:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's not personal, Sonny.\NIt's strictly business.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.89,1:15:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's as cold as they come. Impossible to\Ntrace, so you don't worry about prints.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.27,1:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I put a special tape on the trigger\Nand the butt. Try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.50,1:15:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Is the trigger too tight?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.04,1:15:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My ears!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.59,1:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I left it noisy, so it scares away any\Npain-in-the-ass innocent bystanders.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.22,1:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You've shot them both.\NNow what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.97,1:16:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sit down, finish my dinner.\N- Don't fool around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.14,1:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let your hand drop to your side\Nand let the gun slip out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.81,1:16:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Everybody will still think you've got it.\NThey'll stare at your face,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.24,1:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}so walk out fast, but don't run.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.28,1:16:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't look anybody in the eye,\Nbut don't look away either.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.91,1:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They'll be scared stiff,\Nso don't worry about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.29,1:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You'll be all right. You'll take a vacation,\Nnobody knows where,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.71,1:16:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and we'll catch the hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.38,1:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How bad do you think it will be?\N- Pretty goddamn bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.30,1:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All the other families will probably\Nline up against us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.14,1:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}These things have to happen every five,\Nten years. Gets rid of the bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.35,1:16:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Been ten years since the last one.\NYou have to stop them at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.73,1:16:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Like they should have stopped Hitler in\NMunich, not letting him get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.65,1:17:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You know, Mike, we were all proud\Nof you. Being a hero and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.28,1:17:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your father too.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.99,1:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nothing. Not a hint. Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.49,1:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Even Sollozzo's people don't know\Nwhere the meeting will be held.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.96,1:17:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How much time do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.04,1:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They're going to pick you up outside\NJack Dempsey's in an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.76,1:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- We could put a tail on them.\N- Sollozzo would lose our ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.06,1:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What about the negotiator?\N- He's playing pinochle with my men.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.85,1:18:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He's happy. They're letting him win.\N- Too risky. Maybe we should call it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.15,1:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The negotiator plays cards\Nuntil Mike is back safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.82,1:18:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He could blast whoever is in the car.\N- They'll expect that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.66,1:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sollozzo might not even be\Nin the car, Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.12,1:18:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.69,1:18:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Louis' restaurant in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.98,1:19:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Is it reliable?\N- My man in McCluskey's precinct.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.32,1:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A police captain is on call 24 hours\Na day. He'll be there between 8 and 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.28,1:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Anybody know this joint?\N- Sure, I do. It's perfect for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.33,1:19:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A small family place, good food.\NEveryone minds his business. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.54,1:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They've got an old-fashioned toilet.\NYou know, the box and the chain thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.01,1:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We might be able to tape the gun\Nbehind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.93,1:19:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All right. Mike, you go to the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.68,1:19:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}you eat, talk for a while, you relax.\NMake them relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.73,1:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then you go to take a leak. No, better\Nstill, you ask permission to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.94,1:19:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then you come back blasting.\NTwo shots in the head apiece.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.86,1:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want somebody very good\Nto plant that gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.87,1:19:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't want him coming out\Nwith just his dick.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.08,1:19:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- The gun will be there.\N- You drive him and pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.96,1:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.09,1:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Did he tell you to drop the gun\Nright away?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.39,1:20:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah, a million times.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.77,1:20:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't forget. Two shots apiece in\Nthe head as soon as you come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.65,1:20:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How long do you think it will be\Nbefore I can come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.99,1:20:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}At least a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.54,1:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll square it with Mom, that you're not\Nseeing her before you leave and...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.62,1:20:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll get a message to that girlfriend\Nwhen the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.38,1:20:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.85,1:20:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take care, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.09,1:21:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm glad you came. I hope we can\Nstraighten everything out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.35,1:21:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's not the way I wanted things to go.\NIt should never have happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.31,1:21:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want to straighten everything out.\NI don't want my father bothered again.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.98,1:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I swear on my children\Nthat he won't be, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.15,1:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But you have to keep an open mind\Nwhen we talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.61,1:21:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I hope you're not a hothead like Sonny.\NYou can't talk business with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.37,1:21:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.42,1:22:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm sorry about the other night, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.13,1:22:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I've got to frisk you, so turn around.\NOn your knees, facing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.18,1:22:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I guess I'm getting too old for my job.\NToo grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.18,1:22:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Can't stand the aggravation.\NYou know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.36,1:22:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.51,1:22:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Going to Jersey?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.18,1:23:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.04,1:23:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Nice work, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.04,1:24:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How's the food in this restaurant?\N- Try the veal. It's the best in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.67,1:24:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.83,1:24:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm going to speak Italian to Mikey.\N- Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.54,1:26:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What I want...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.42,1:26:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's most important to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.17,1:26:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...is that I have a guarantee.\NNo more attempts on my father's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.80,1:26:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What guarantees can I give you?\NI'm the hunted one!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.14,1:26:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I missed my chance.\NYou think too much of me, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.81,1:26:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm not that clever.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.31,1:26:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All I want is a truce.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.20,1:26:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have to go to the bathroom.\NIs it all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.33,1:26:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When you got to go, you got to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.50,1:27:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.25,1:27:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.59,1:27:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I've frisked a thousand punks.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.14,1:32:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Okay, you take over.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.36,1:32:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I love you, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.91,1:32:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm sorry, Pa. He doesn't know you yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.08,1:32:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hey, big guy. Give it to Grandpa.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.38,1:32:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}"I hope you get well, Grandpa, and wish\NI see you soon. Your grandson Frank."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.76,1:32:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.10,1:32:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take them downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.27,1:32:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go on, Carlo, you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.98,1:32:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.00,1:33:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What's the matter with you, Carlo?\N- Shut up and set the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.73,1:33:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Since McCluskey's killing, the police\Nhave cracked down on our operations.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.53,1:33:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And also the other families.\NThere's been a lot of bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.79,1:33:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They hit us, so we hit them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.71,1:33:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Through our newspaper contacts\Nwe've been able to put out material
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.50,1:34:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}about McCluskey's link with Sollozzo\Nin the drug rackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.97,1:34:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So things are loosening up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.14,1:34:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I sent Fredo to Las Vegas, under\Nthe protection of Don Francesco of L.A.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.98,1:34:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I want him to rest.\N- I'm going to learn the casino business.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.99,1:34:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where's Michael?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.55,1:34:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It was Michael who killed Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.59,1:34:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But he's safe. We're starting to work\Nto bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.99,1:35:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Did you find out where that old pimp\NTattaglia is hiding? I want him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.83,1:35:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny, things are starting to loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.13,1:35:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you go after Tattaglia, all hell\Nwill break loose. Pop can negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.13,1:35:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He must get better first. I'll decide...\N- War is costly. We can't do business.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.10,1:35:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Neither can they. Don't worry about it!\N- We can't afford a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.14,1:35:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- No more stalemate. I'll kill the bastard!\N- You're getting a great reputation!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.31,1:35:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do as I say! If I had a Sicilian wartime\Nconsigliere, I wouldn't be in this shape!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.19,1:35:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Pop had Genco. Look what I got.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.74,1:35:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm sorry. I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.41,1:35:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Ma made a little dinner. It's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.21,1:36:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Niggers are having a good time\Nwith our policy banks in Harlem.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.92,1:36:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Driving new Cadillacs,\Npaying 50 per cent on a bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.05,1:36:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's because they've started\Nmaking big money.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.34,1:36:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Poppa never talked business\Nat the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.97,1:36:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Shut up, Connie...\N- Don't you ever tell her to shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.64,1:36:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.69,1:36:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'd like to talk to you after dinner.\NI could do more for the family...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.03,1:36:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We don't discuss business at the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.91,1:37:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I kiss your hand, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.50,1:37:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why are you so far\Nfrom the house?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.71,1:37:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You know I'm responsible to your\Nfather for your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.67,1:37:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The bodyguards are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.97,1:37:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's still dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.51,1:37:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We've heard from Santino\Nin New York...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.39,1:37:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your enemies know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.85,1:37:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Did Santino say when\NI can go back?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.27,1:37:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.15,1:37:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.90,1:37:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.37,1:37:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take my car.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.29,1:38:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want to walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.71,1:38:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.16,1:38:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where have all the men gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.04,1:38:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They're all dead from vendettas.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.96,1:38:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There are the names of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.14,1:39:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, hey, take me to the America, G.I.!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.11,1:39:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, hey, take me to the America, G.I.!\NClark Gable!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.57,1:39:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}America! Take me to the America, G.I.!\NClark Gable, Rita Hayworth!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.05,1:39:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mamma mia what a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.10,1:39:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I think you got hit\Nby the thunderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.90,1:39:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In Sicily women are more\Ndangerous than shotguns.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.97,1:40:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Did you have a good hunt?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.35,1:40:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You know all the girls\Naround here?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.14,1:40:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We saw some real beauties.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.90,1:40:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}One of them struck our friend\Nlike a thunderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.45,1:40:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She would tempt the devil himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.96,1:40:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Really put together.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.75,1:40:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Such hair, such mouth!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.13,1:41:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The girls around here are\Nbeautiful...but virtuous.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.85,1:41:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This one had a purple dress...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.56,1:41:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And a purple ribbon in her hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.31,1:41:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A type more Greek than Italian.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.40,1:41:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.36,1:41:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There's no girl like that\Nin this town.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.91,1:41:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My God, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.42,1:41:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.17,1:41:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.01,1:41:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.63,1:41:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tell him to come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.97,1:41:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Call him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.87,1:42:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Fabrizio, you translate.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.04,1:42:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I apologise if I offended you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.34,1:42:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm a stranger in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.51,1:42:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I meant no disrespect\Nto you or your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.22,1:42:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm an American, hiding in Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.31,1:42:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My name is Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.69,1:42:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There are people who'd pay a lot\Nof money for that information.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.86,1:42:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But then your daughter\Nwould lose a father...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.66,1:42:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...instead of gaining a husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.09,1:42:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want to meet your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.17,1:43:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}With your permission, and under\Nthe supervision of your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.30,1:43:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}With all respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.43,1:43:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come to my house Sunday morning.\NMy name is Vitelli.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.44,1:43:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.41,1:46:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll knock you dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.34,1:46:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Save it for the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.13,1:46:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We've got to pick up my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.78,1:46:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.03,1:46:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.50,1:47:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- It was my fault!\N- Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.21,1:47:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It was my fault. I hit him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.17,1:47:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I started a fight with him.\NI hit him, so he hit me...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.22,1:47:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm just going to get a doctor\Nto take a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.31,1:47:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny, please don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.60,1:47:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter with you?\NWhat am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.90,1:47:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Make that baby an orphan\Nbefore he's born?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.24,1:47:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You spic slobs still betting Yankees?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.45,1:47:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tell them to stop taking in action.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.99,1:47:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We lost enough money last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.88,1:47:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come here, come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.85,1:48:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you touch my sister again, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.42,1:52:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey! We weren't expecting you, Kay.\NYou should call.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.76,1:52:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yes, I have. I've tried writing and calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.14,1:52:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I want to reach Michael.\N- Nobody knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.10,1:52:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All we know is that he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.02,1:53:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What was that?\N- An accident, but nobody was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.24,1:53:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom, will you give this letter to Michael.\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.66,1:53:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If I accepted that, a court could prove\NI have knowledge of his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.33,1:53:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He'll get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.83,1:53:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I let my cab go, so can I call\Nanother one, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.59,1:53:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come on. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.86,1:53:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hello?\N- Is Carlo there?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.15,1:53:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Who is this?\N- A friend of Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.70,1:53:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tell him that I can't make it tonight\Nuntil later.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.83,1:54:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.46,1:54:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Dinner's on the table.\N- I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.13,1:54:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- The food is getting cold.\N- I'll eat out later.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.47,1:54:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You just told me to make you dinner!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.19,1:54:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She has a filthy mouth, this Guinea brat.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.28,1:54:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's it, break it all, you spoiled\NGuinea brat. Break it all!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.66,1:54:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why don't you bring your whore\Nhome for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.92,1:54:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Maybe I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.05,1:54:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Clean it up!\N- Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.35,1:55:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You skinny, spoiled brat.\NClean it up! Clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.77,1:55:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Clean it up! I said, clean it up!\NClean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.19,1:55:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Clean it up. Clean that up, you...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.07,1:55:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Clean it!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.16,1:55:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Clean it up! Yeah, kill me.\NBe a murderer, like your father!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.50,1:55:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- All you Corleones are murderers!\N- I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.12,1:55:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come on, kill me!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.17,1:55:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.05,1:55:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I hate you!\N- Now I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.47,1:55:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You Guinea brat. Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.52,1:55:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Connie, what's the matter?\NI can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.65,1:55:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Connie, talk louder. The baby's crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.86,1:55:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Santino, I can't understand.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.99,1:55:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.79,1:56:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You wait there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.13,1:56:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, you just wait there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.88,1:56:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Son-of-a-bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.51,1:56:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Son-of-a-bitch!\N- What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.35,1:56:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Open the goddamn gate!\NGet off your ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.48,1:56:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sonny!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.28,1:56:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Sonny.\N- Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.33,1:56:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go after him, go on!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.86,1:57:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Son-of-a-bitch. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.72,1:59:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Give me a drop.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.90,1:59:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My wife is crying upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.53,1:59:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I hear cars coming to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.58,1:59:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Consigliere of mine,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.87,1:59:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}tell your Don what everyone\Nseems to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.46,1:59:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I didn't tell Mama anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.80,1:59:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I was about to come up and wake you\Nand tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.39,1:59:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But you needed a drink first.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.22,1:59:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.48,1:59:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, now you've had your drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.49,2:00:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They shot Sonny on the causeway.\NHe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.97,2:00:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want no inquiries made.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.60,2:00:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want no acts of vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.73,2:00:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to arrange a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.52,2:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...with the heads of the five families.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.15,2:00:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This war stops now.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.13,2:01:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Call Bonasera.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.68,2:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I need him now.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.11,2:01:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This is Tom Hagen. I'm calling for\NVito Corleone, at his request.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.45,2:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You owe your Don a service.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.08,2:01:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He has no doubt that you will repay it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.70,2:01:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He will be at your funeral parlour\Nin one hour. Be there to greet him.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.19,2:02:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, my friend, are you ready\Nto do me this service?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.23,2:02:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yes. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.50,2:02:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to use all your powers\Nand all your skills.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.13,2:02:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't want his mother\Nto see him this way.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.19,2:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Look how they massacred my boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.56,2:03:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's safer to teach you English!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.81,2:03:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I know English...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.60,2:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Monday, Tuesday, Thursday,\NWednesday, Friday, Sunday, Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.28,2:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Greetings, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.91,2:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How are things in Palermo?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.75,2:03:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael is teaching me to\Ndrive...watch, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.17,2:03:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How are things in Palermo?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.93,2:03:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Young people don't respect\Nanything any more...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.01,2:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}times are changing for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.27,2:04:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This place has become\Ntoo dangerous for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.23,2:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to move to a villa\Nnear Siracusa...right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.79,2:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.58,2:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Bad news from America.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.46,2:04:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your brother, Santino,\Nthey killed him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.93,2:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let's go...you promised.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.82,2:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get the car.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.08,2:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Are you driving yourself, Boss?\NIs your wife coming with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.46,2:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, take her to her father's house\Nuntil things are safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.21,2:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Okay, anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.30,2:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Calo, where is Apollonia?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.89,2:05:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She's going to surprise you.\NShe wants to drive.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.64,2:05:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She'll make a good American wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.40,2:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Wait, I'll get the baggage.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.49,2:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Fabrizio!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.16,2:05:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.50,2:05:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Wait there! I'll drive to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.80,2:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, Apollonia!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.45,2:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Barzini, I want to thank you\Nfor helping me organise this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.33,2:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and the other heads of the five families\Nfrom New York and New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.84,2:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Carmine Cuneo from the Bronx,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.13,2:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and from Brooklyn...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.05,2:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...Philip Tattaglia.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:45.72,2:06:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And from Staten Island
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.89,2:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}we have with us Victor Strachi.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.48,2:06:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And the other associates that came as\Nfar as from California and Kansas City
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.40,2:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and all the other territories\Nof the country. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.62,2:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How did things ever get so far?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.17,2:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.88,2:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It was so unfortunate, so unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.51,2:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tattaglia lost a son, and I lost a son.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.35,2:07:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're quits. And if Tattaglia agrees,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.06,2:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}then I'm willing to let things go on\Nas before.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.32,2:07:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're grateful to Don Corleone\Nfor calling this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.11,2:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We all know him as a man of his word.\NA modest man who listens to reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.45,2:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yes, Don Barzini. He's too modest.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.58,2:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He had all the judges and politicians\Nin his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.88,2:07:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He refused to share them.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.17,2:08:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When did I ever refuse\Nan accommodation?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.88,2:08:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All of you know me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:05.14,2:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When did I ever refuse,\Nexcept one time? And why?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.98,2:08:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Because I believe this drug business\Nwill destroy us in the years to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.98,2:08:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's not like gambling or liquor\Nor even women,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.07,2:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}which is something that most people\Nwant, but is forbidden by the Church.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.33,2:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Even the police that have helped us in\Nthe past with gambling and other things
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.21,2:08:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}are going to refuse to help us\Nwhen it comes to narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.46,2:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I believed that then...\Nand I believe that now.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.67,2:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.97,2:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's not like the old days,\Nwhen we could do anything we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.85,2:08:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}A refusal is not the act of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.81,2:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If Don Corleone had all the judges and\Npoliticians, then he must share them
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.40,2:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}or let others use them. He must let us\Ndraw the water from the well.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.86,2:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Certainly he can present a bill\Nfor such services.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.66,2:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}After all, we're not communists.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.16,2:09:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I also don't believe in drugs.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.46,2:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}For years I paid my people extra, so\Nthey wouldn't do that kind of business.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.46,2:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Somebody says to them\N"I have powders."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.76,2:09:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}"If you put up 3-4,000 dollar investment,\Nwe can make 50,000 distributing."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.10,2:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They can't resist. I want to control it\Nas a business, keep it respectable.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.10,2:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't want it near schools,\NI don't want it sold to children.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.23,2:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's an infámia.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.24,2:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In my city we would keep the traffic\Nto the coloured.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.24,2:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They're animals,\Nso let them lose their souls.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.04,2:10:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I hoped that we could come here\Nand reason together.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.96,2:10:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I'm willing to do whatever is\Nnecessary to find a peaceful solution.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.22,2:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We are agreed. The traffic in drugs\Nwill be permitted, but controlled.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.93,2:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone will give us protection\Nin the east, and there will be peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.52,2:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I must have strict assurance\Nfrom Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.11,2:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}As time goes by and his position\Nbecomes stronger,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.78,2:10:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}will he attempt any individual vendetta?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.45,2:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We are all reasonable men.\NWe don't have to give assurances.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.83,2:10:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You talk about vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.25,2:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Will vengeance bring your son\Nback to you?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.54,2:10:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Or my boy to me?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.50,2:10:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I forgo the vengeance of my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.01,2:10:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I have selfish reasons.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.51,2:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My youngest son was forced\Nto leave this country...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.98,2:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...because of this Sollozzo business.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.19,2:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I have to make arrangements\Nto bring him back here safely.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.20,2:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Cleared of all these false charges.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.28,2:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I'm a superstitious man.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.54,2:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If an unlucky accident should befall him,\Nif he should be shot by a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.21,2:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}or if he should hang himself\Nin his jail cell,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.88,2:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}or if he's struck by a bolt of lightning,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.01,2:11:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}then I'm going to blame\Nsome of the people in this room.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.10,2:11:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And that I do not forgive.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.10,2:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But, that aside...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.40,2:11:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...Iet me say that I swear...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:50.44,2:11:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...on the souls of my grandchildren,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.74,2:11:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}that I will not be the one to break\Nthe peace we've made here today.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.48,2:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Should I insist that all of Tattaglia's\Ndrug middlemen have clean records?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:29.15,2:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mention it. Don't insist.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.28,2:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Barzini will know without being told.\N- You mean Tattaglia.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.83,2:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tattaglia's a pimp. He could never\Nhave outfought Santino.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.54,2:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I didn't know until this day\Nthat it was Barzini all along.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:09.27,2:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come on, Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.65,2:13:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Keep together, everyone. Brian.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.57,2:13:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Okay, all right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.63,2:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}How long have you been back?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.42,2:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I've been back a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.76,2:13:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Longer than that, I think.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.35,2:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's good to see you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:55.65,2:13:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm working for my father now, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.78,2:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's been sick. Very sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.29,2:14:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But you're not like him. You told me you\Nweren't going to become like your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.05,2:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My father is no different\Nthan any other powerful man.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:17.63,2:14:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Any man who's responsible\Nfor other people.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.26,2:14:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Like a senator or president.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.68,2:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How naive you sound.\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.35,2:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They don't have men killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:33.07,2:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Who's being naive, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.65,2:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}My father's way of doing things is over.\NEven he knows that.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.32,2:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}In five years the Corleone family\Nis going to be completely legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.33,2:14:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Trust me. That's all I can tell you\Nabout my business. Kay...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.71,2:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael, why did you come here? Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.26,2:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What do you want with me after all\Nthis time? I've been calling and writing.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.22,2:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I came because I need you.\NI care for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.81,2:15:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Please stop it, Michael.\N- Because... I want you to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.31,2:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- It's too late.\N- Please, Kay...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:16.57,2:15:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll do anything you ask to make up for\Nwhat's happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.57,2:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Because that's important, Kay.\NBecause what's important is that...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.29,2:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...we have each other.\NThat we have a life together.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.00,2:15:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That we have children. Our children.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.46,2:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Kay, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.47,2:15:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:05.16,2:16:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Barzini's people chisel my territory\Nand we do nothing about it!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.12,2:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Soon I'll have no place to hang my hat!\N- Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.79,2:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm not asking for help.\NJust take off the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.09,2:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Be patient.\N- We must protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.34,2:16:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Let me recruit some new men.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.93,2:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Barzini would get an excuse to fight.\N- Mike, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.18,2:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don Corleone...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.10,2:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You once said that one day Tessio\Nand me could form our own family.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.73,2:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Till today I would never think of it.\NI must ask your permission.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.28,2:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael is now head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:42.53,2:16:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If he gives his permission,\Nthen you have my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:46.91,2:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}After we make the move to Nevada
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.16,2:16:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}you can leave the Corleone family\Nand go on your own.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.87,2:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How long will that be?\N- Six months.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.21,2:17:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Forgive me, but with you gone, me and\NPete will come under Barzini's thumb.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.51,2:17:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I hate that Barzini. In six months' time\Nthere will be nothing left to build on.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:10.18,2:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Do you have faith in my judgement?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:13.35,2:17:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Do I have your loyalty?\N- Always, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.35,2:17:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Then be a friend to Michael.\NDo as he says.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:24.24,2:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Things are negotiated that'll solve your\Nproblems and answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.91,2:17:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's all I can tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.04,2:17:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Carlo, you grew up in Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.54,2:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}When we make our move there,\Nyou'll be my right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.13,2:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom Hagen is no longer consigliere.\NHe'll be our lawyer in Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.01,2:17:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's no reflection on Tom,\Njust how I want it.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.68,2:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If I ever need help, who's a better\Nconsigliere than my father? That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.91,2:18:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Thank you, Poppa.\N- I'm happy for you, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:15.25,2:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mike... Why am I out?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.67,2:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You're not a wartime consigliere, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.71,2:18:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Things may get rough with the move.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:27.01,2:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:33.43,2:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I advised Michael. I never thought\Nyou were a bad consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.81,2:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I thought Santino was a bad Don,\Nrest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.40,2:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael has all my confidence,\Njust as you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.70,2:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But there are reasons why you must\Nhave no part in what is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.37,2:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Maybe I could help.\N- You're out, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:46.88,2:19:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I can't get over the way your face looks.\NSo good!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:51.30,2:19:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This doctor did some job. Did Kay\Ntalk you into it? Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.97,2:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Leave them out here.\NHe's tired and wants to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.56,2:20:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let me open the door, all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.65,2:20:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hello, Mike! Welcome to Las Vegas!\N- All for you, kid! It's all his idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.57,2:20:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Your brother Freddy.\N- Girls?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.66,2:20:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll be right back. Keep them occupied.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.13,2:20:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Anything you want, kid, anything.\N- Who are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:29.80,2:20:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- That's for you to find out.\N- Get rid of them, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.84,2:20:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Hey, Mike...\N- I'm here on business. Get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.72,2:20:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm tired. Get rid of the band too.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.19,2:20:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, take off. Take off. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.49,2:20:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, that's it. Hey, Angelo.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.36,2:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, come on! Scram!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.16,2:21:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come on, honey. I don't know\Nwhat's the matter with him, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.83,2:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.13,2:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't know. He's tired.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.68,2:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What happened to Moe Greene?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.80,2:21:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He had some business. He said to\Ngive him a call when the party started.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.39,2:21:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:26.56,2:21:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Johnny, how are you?\N- Nice to see you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.11,2:21:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- We're proud of you.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.36,2:21:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sit down, I want to talk to you.\NThe Don is proud too.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.99,2:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well, I owe it all to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:38.91,2:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He knows how grateful you are. That's\Nwhy he'd like to ask a favour of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.21,2:21:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mike, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.25,2:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're thinking of giving up our interests\Nin the olive oil business and settle here.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.51,2:21:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Moe will sell us his share of the casino\Nand the hotel, so we'll own all of it. Tom!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.60,2:22:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Are you sure? Moe loves the business.\NHe never said nothing about selling.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.85,2:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll make him an offer he can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.02,2:22:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}See, Johnny...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:11.48,2:22:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We figure that entertainment\Nwould draw gamblers to the casino.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:15.90,2:22:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We hope you'll sign a contract\Nto appear five times a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.37,2:22:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Perhaps convince some of your friends\Nin the movies to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.25,2:22:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.42,2:22:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sure, Mike. I'll do anything\Nfor my godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:36.51,2:22:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.26,2:22:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hey, Mike! Hello, fellows.\NEverybody's here. Freddy, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.01,2:22:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Good to see you.\N- How are you, Moe?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.27,2:22:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Have everything? Specially prepared\Nfood, the best dancers, and good credit.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:51.65,2:22:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Draw chips for everybody,\Nso they can play on the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.74,2:23:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Is my credit good enough\Nto buy you out?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.28,2:23:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Buy me out?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.87,2:23:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The casino, the hotel. The\NCorleone family wants to buy you out.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.92,2:23:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The Corleone family wants to\Nbuy me out? No, I buy you out.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.55,2:23:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your casino loses money.\NWe can do better.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.88,2:23:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You think I'm skimming off the top?\N- You're unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:27.64,2:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You Guineas make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.35,2:23:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I took Freddy in when you had a bad\Ntime, and now you try to push me out!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.98,2:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You did that because we bankrolled\Nyour casino
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.95,2:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and the Molinari family guaranteed\Nhis safety. Let's talk business.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.16,2:23:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Yes. First of all, you're all done. You\Ndon't have that kind of muscle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:50.54,2:23:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}The Godfather is sick. You're getting\Nchased out of New York by the others.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.09,2:23:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do you think you can come to my hotel\Nand take over?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.01,2:24:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I talked to Barzini. I can make a deal\Nwith him and still keep my hotel!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.14,2:24:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Is that why you slapped my brother\Naround in public?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.72,2:24:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That was nothing, Mike.\NMoe didn't mean nothing by that.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:12.69,2:24:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He flies off the handle sometimes,\Nbut we're good friends.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.02,2:24:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have a business to run.\NI've got to kick asses sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.74,2:24:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We had an argument,\Nso I had to straighten him out.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.82,2:24:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You straightened my brother out?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:28.58,2:24:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He was banging cocktail waitresses!\NPlayers couldn't get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.25,2:24:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.84,2:24:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I leave for New York tomorrow.\NThink about a price.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:43.88,2:24:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Son-of-a-bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:45.59,2:24:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm Moe Greene! I made my bones\Nwhen you were out with cheerleaders.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:51.14,2:24:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Wait a minute, Moe. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.69,2:24:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom, you're the consigliere.\NTalk to the Don...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.40,2:25:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Just a minute. Don is semi-retired and\NMike is in charge of the family business.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:03.65,2:25:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}If you have anything to say,\Nsay it to Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:10.70,2:25:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mike, you don't come to Las Vegas and\Ntalk to a man like Moe Greene like that!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.63,2:25:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Fredo...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.88,2:25:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You're my older brother, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.01,2:25:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But don't ever take sides with anyone\Nagainst the family again.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.81,2:25:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I have to see my father and his people,\Nso have dinner without me.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.70,2:25:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This weekend we'll go out. We'll go to\Nthe city, see a show and have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.87,2:25:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Your sister wants to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:00.09,2:26:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Let her ask.\N- She's afraid to.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:02.46,2:26:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They want you to be godfather\Nto their boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:05.34,2:26:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- We'll see.\N- Will you?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.59,2:26:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Let me think about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.27,2:26:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Barzini will move against you first.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:21.48,2:26:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He'll set up a meeting with someone\Nyou absolutely trust.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:26.07,2:26:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Guaranteeing your safety.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.24,2:26:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And at that meeting\Nyou'll be assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:36.91,2:26:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I like to drink wine more than I used to.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:41.34,2:26:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Anyway, I'm drinking more.\N- It's good for you, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:49.97,2:26:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:53.35,2:26:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Are you happy with your wife\Nand children?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:57.23,2:27:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Very happy.\N- That's good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.94,2:27:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I hope you don't mind the way I keep\Ngoing over this Barzini business.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:07.07,2:27:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- No, not at all.\N- It's an old habit.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:11.37,2:27:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I spend my life trying not to be careless.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.95,2:27:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Women and children can be careless,\Nbut not men.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.71,2:27:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- How's your boy?\N- He's good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.25,2:27:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He looks more like you every day.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.72,2:27:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He's smarter than I am. He's three\Nand can read the funny papers.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:37.18,2:27:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Read the funny papers.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.36,2:27:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to arrange for a telephone\Nman to check all in- and out-going calls.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:52.28,2:27:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I did it already. I took care of that, Pop.\N- That's right. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.58,2:28:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:04.46,2:28:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}What's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:09.80,2:28:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll handle it. I told you I can handle it,\Nso I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.73,2:28:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I knew that Santino would have to\Ngo through all this.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.15,2:28:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And Fredo...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.62,2:28:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Fredo was, well...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:40.45,2:28:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I never wanted this for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.54,2:28:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I worked my whole life. I don't apologise\Nfor taking care of my family.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.84,2:28:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And I refused to be a fool,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:54.93,2:28:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}dancing on a string\Nheld by all those big shots.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:00.89,2:29:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I don't apologise. That's my life,\Nbut I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.98,2:29:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}...that when it was your time, you would\Nbe the one to hold the strings.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.07,2:29:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Senator Corleone. Governor Corleone.\NSomething.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:18.78,2:29:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Another pezzo da novanta.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:21.95,2:29:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Well...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.58,2:29:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Just wasn't enough time, Michael.\NWasn't enough time.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.84,2:29:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We'll get there, Pop. We'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.05,2:29:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Now listen, whoever comes to you\Nwith this Barzini meeting,
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.68,2:29:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}he's the traitor. Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.54,2:30:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Can I hold it, please?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:20.72,2:30:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Can I water these?\N- Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:24.81,2:30:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.44,2:30:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Be careful. You're spilling it.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.32,2:30:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Antony!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.57,2:30:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:46.33,2:30:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's it. We'll put it right there.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.01,2:30:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll show you something. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:59.55,2:31:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Stand there.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:05.02,2:31:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Give me an orange!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.54,2:31:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:28.21,2:31:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You run in there. Run in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:43.89,2:31:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.57,2:34:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Mike, can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:55.96,2:34:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Barzini wants to arrange a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:58.46,2:35:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}He says we can straighten out\Nany of our problems.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:02.63,2:35:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You talked to him?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:05.97,2:35:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I can arrange security. On my territory.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:12.93,2:35:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- All right?\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:33.08,2:35:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do you know how they're going to\Ncome at you?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:38.46,2:35:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}They're arranging a meeting\Nin Brooklyn. Tessio's ground.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:44.13,2:35:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Where I'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:58.31,2:36:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I always thought it would be\NClemenza, not Tessio.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:02.23,2:36:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It's the smart move.\NTessio was always smarter.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:08.61,2:36:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But I'm going to wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:10.91,2:36:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}After the baptism.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.91,2:36:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I've decided to be godfather\Nto Connie's baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:18.75,2:36:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And then I'll meet with Don Barzini
Dialogue: 0,2:36:22.00,2:36:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}and Tattaglia.\NAll the heads of the five families.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.56,2:38:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael, do you believe in God, the\NFather, Creator of Heaven and Earth?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:53.03,2:38:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:54.57,2:38:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do you believe in Jesus Christ,\NHis only Son, our Lord?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:58.16,2:38:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:59.70,2:39:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Do you believe in the Holy Ghost,\Nthe Holy Catholic Church?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:03.83,2:39:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:10.02,2:40:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael Francis Rizzi,\Ndo you renounce Satan?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:21.03,2:40:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I do renounce him.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:32.08,2:40:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And all his works?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:46.85,2:40:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I do renounce them.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:49.81,2:40:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:54.27,2:40:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- And all his pomps?\N- I do renounce them.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:13.62,2:41:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael Rizzi, will you be baptised?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:17.63,2:41:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:26.14,2:41:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael Rizzi, go in peace, and may\Nthe Lord be with you. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:45.70,2:41:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Kay!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:47.95,2:41:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Kiss your godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.14,2:42:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Can't go to Vegas. Something's come\Nup. Everybody has to leave without us.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:20.19,2:42:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Mike, it's our first vacation!\N- Connie, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:23.74,2:42:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go back to the house, wait for my call.\NIt's important.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:28.07,2:42:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll only be a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:46.51,2:42:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}We're on our way to Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:50.76,2:42:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I hope Mike can get us a good deal.\N- I'm sure he will.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:02.40,2:43:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Sal, Tom, the boss says he'll come in a\Nseparate car, so you two go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:07.95,2:43:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- That screws up my arrangements.\N- That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:11.74,2:43:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I can't go either, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:25.63,2:43:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tell Mike it was only business.\NI always liked him.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:30.80,2:43:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- He understands that.\N- Excuse me, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:40.19,2:43:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom, can you get me off the hook?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:43.65,2:43:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- For old times' sake?\N- Can't do it, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:32.41,2:44:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You have to answer for Santino, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:40.29,2:44:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Mike, you got it all wrong.\N- You fingered Sonny for Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:45.13,2:44:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That little farce you played\Nwith my sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:48.96,2:44:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- You think that could fool a Corleone?\N- I'm innocent. I swear on the kids.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:54.22,2:44:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Please, don't do this.\N- Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:59.73,2:45:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't do this to me, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:11.20,2:45:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Barzini is dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.95,2:45:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}So is Philip Tattaglia.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:18.58,2:45:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Moe Greene.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:21.00,2:45:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Strachi. Cuneo.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:26.67,2:45:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Today I settle all family business,\Nso don't tell me you're innocent, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:32.05,2:45:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Admit what you did.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:37.72,2:45:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Get him a drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:45.81,2:45:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:48.32,2:45:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't be afraid, Carlo. Do you think\NI'd make my sister a widow?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:54.82,2:45:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'm godfather to your son, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:04.42,2:46:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Go ahead, drink, drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:11.51,2:46:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No, you're out of the family business.\NThat's your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:16.34,2:46:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You're finished.\NI'm putting you on a plane to Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:20.47,2:46:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:26.10,2:46:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I want you to stay there. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:30.07,2:46:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Only don't tell me you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:33.61,2:46:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Because it insults my intelligence.\NMakes me very angry.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:42.16,2:46:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Who approached you?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:45.46,2:46:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Tattaglia or Barzini?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:55.47,2:46:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}It was Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:01.43,2:47:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:09.10,2:47:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}There's a car waiting outside\Nto take you to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:13.44,2:47:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}I'll call your wife and tell her\Nwhat flight you're on.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:21.83,2:47:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Mike...\N- Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:49.60,2:47:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hello, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:50.04,2:48:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- I'm trying to tell you...\N- Mama, please!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:03.18,2:49:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:05.01,2:49:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- What is it?\N- Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:09.48,2:49:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael, you lousy bastard!\NYou killed my husband.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:14.69,2:49:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You waited until Papa died,\Nso nobody could stop you.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:18.86,2:49:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}You blamed him for Sonny.\NEverybody did.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:22.15,2:49:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}But you never thought about me!\NNow what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:28.37,2:49:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Connie.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:31.71,2:49:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Why do you think he kept Carlo at the\NMall? He knew he was going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:37.46,2:49:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}And you stood godfather to our baby.\NYou lousy cold-hearted bastard!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:43.18,2:49:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Want to know how many men he had\Nkilled with Carlo? Read the papers!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:47.47,2:49:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}That's your husband,\Nthat's your husband!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:59.57,2:50:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}No! No, no...
Dialogue: 0,2:50:03.61,2:50:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Take her upstairs. Get her a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:28.30,2:50:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}She's hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:34.69,2:50:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:38.44,2:50:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Michael, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:42.03,2:50:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}- Don't ask me about my business, Kay.\N- Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:45.86,2:50:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}Don't ask me about my business.\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,2:51:08.59,2:51:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:12.93,2:51:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This one time.
Dialogue: 0,2:51:18.69,2:51:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fncalibri\fs19\bord6\fsp0\3a&h9f\c&HC05bdfa&\be77}This one time I'll let you ask me\Nabout my affairs.
